Alpha Arbutin:
Alpha arbutin is a plant extract that has been shown to have skin-brightening properties. It is a type of hydroquinone that is less harsh than traditional hydroquinone. Alpha arbutin is beneficial for those with hyperpigmentation or skin discoloration.

Ascorbic Acid:
Ascorbic acid, also known as vitamin C, is a powerful antioxidant that can provide multiple benefits to the skin. It can boost collagen production, improve skin texture, reduce fine lines and wrinkles, and brighten dull or unevenly pigmented skin.
